AutoCAD Drawing File (DWG)
Plumbing Systems Layout
Date: 2026-03-04
Version: 2.5

BUILDING PLUMBING DISTRIBUTION
=================================

Main Water Supply:
- Inlet Point: Single 50mm diameter entry
- Pressure Tank: 5000L capacity (Basement)
- Backup Pump: 25 L/s capacity
- Pressure Reduction: 200-400 kPa maintained

Hot Water System:
- Capacity: 2000L storage tank
- Element Size: 80 kW heating elements
- Temperature: 50-60°C (thermostat controlled)
- Distribution: Copper piping, insulated

Cold Water Distribution:
- Primary Loop: 40mm (main risers)
- Branches: 25mm to 15mm (fixture branches)
- Material: Copper or HDPE
- Velocity: 0.6-2.0 m/s throughout

Plumbing Fixtures:
- Toilets: 2 per floor (15 floors) = 30 total
- Sinks: 120+ (office, restroom, kitchen)
- Showers: 6 (emergency eye wash + facilities)
- Urinals: 8 (optional waterless)

Drainage System:
- Waste Water Pump: 50 L/s @ 50m TDH
- Sump Pit: 10m³ capacity (basement)
- Grease Trap: Kitchen areas (50L capacity)
- Slope: 1:100 minimum throughout

Fire Protection (Water):
- Storage Tanks: 500,000L capacity
- Sprinkler System: Wet type, 100% coverage
- Pressure: 400-600 kPa at sprinkler heads
- Activation: Automatic 60° thermal fusible
- Manual Call Points: Every 30m corridor

Special Systems:
- Graywater Recycling: 100,000L storage
- Rainwater Harvesting: 500,000L cistern
- Greywater Treatment: Sand filter system
- Reuse Target: 30% of total water consumption

Maintenance Access:
- Valve Locations: Clearly marked + labeled
- Cleanouts: Every change of direction
- Isolation Points: Per floor for maintenance
- Service Lanes: 1.2m minimum clearance

System Testing:
- Pressure Test: 1.5x working pressure, 1 hour
- Leak Test: Tracer dye + pressure gauge
- Flow Test: 3000+ L/day capacity verified
- Certification: PASSED all tests

Compliance:
- AS 3500 Series: Fully compliant
- Building Code: Approved & certified
- Water Quality: Potable grade throughout
- Accessibility: All shut-offs clearly labeled

Drawing Status: APPROVED FOR CONSTRUCTION
